data.description: Wonderful opportunity to own a home in historic Gloucester Courthouse! Don’t miss out on this well maintained 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home conveniently located between Main Street and Beaverdam Park. Corner lot, updated interior/exterior features, kitchen boasts updated cabinetry with granite counters. LVP and hardwood flooring, den with decorative fireplace, separate laundry room and large lot with plenty of room for entertaining or to create your own backyard oasis. Come enjoy Main Street's restaurants, microbrewery, charming shops and Daffodil Festival, all an effortless walk away.
